{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Animation","mdn_url":"/fr/docs/Web/API/Animation","locale":"fr","native":"Français","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/Animation\"><code>Animation</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructeur</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/Animation\"><code>Animation()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Propriétés</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/currentTime\"><code>currentTime</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/effect\"><code>effect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/finished\"><code>finished</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/id\"><code>id</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/pending\"><code>pending</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/playbackRate\"><code>playbackRate</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/playState\"><code>playState</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/ready\"><code>ready</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/replaceState\"><code>replaceState</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/Animation/startTime\"><code>startTime</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/timeline\"><code>timeline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Méthodes</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/cancel\"><code>cancel()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/commitStyles\"><code>commitStyles()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/finish\"><code>finish()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/pause\"><code>pause()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/persist\"><code>persist()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/play\"><code>play()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/reverse\"><code>reverse()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/updatePlaybackRate\"><code>updatePlaybackRate()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Événements</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/cancel_event\"><code>cancel</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/finish_event\"><code>finish</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/remove_event\"><code>remove</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Héritage&nbsp;:</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>Cette fonction est expérimentale</strong><br>Puisque cette fonction est toujours en développement dans certains navigateurs, veuillez consulter le <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">tableau de compatibilité</a> pour les préfixes à utiliser selon les navigateurs.<br>Il convient de noter qu'une fonctionnalité expérimentale peut voir sa syntaxe ou son comportement modifié dans le futur en fonction des évolutions de la spécification.</p></div>\n<p>L'interface <strong><code>Animation</code></strong> de <a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/Web_Animations_API\">l'API Web Animations</a> correspond à un lecteur d'animations et offre les commandes nécessaires au contrôle et à la chronologie d'un noeud ou d'une source d'animation.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"constructeur","title":"Constructeur","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"animation_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/Animation\"><code>Animation()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Crée une nouvelle instance de l'objet <code>Animation</code>.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"propriétés","title":"Propriétés","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"animation.currenttime_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/currentTime\"><code>Animation.currentTime</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>La valeur actuelle de temps de l'animation en millisecondes, que l'animation soit en pause ou en cours. Si l'animation ne possède pas de <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationTimeline\"><code>timeline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, est inactive ou n'a toujours pas été lancée, la valeur est <code>null</code>.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl><!---->\n<dl>\n  <dt id=\"animation.effect_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/effect\"><code>Animation.effect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Récupère et défini le <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/KeyframeEffect\"><code>KeyframeEffect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> associé à cette animation.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"animation.finished_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/finished\"><code>Animation.finished</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"Cette valeur ne peut pas être changée.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Lecture seule </span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Retourne la <code>Promise</code> terminée en cours pour cette animation.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl><!---->\n<dl>\n  <dt id=\"animation.id_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/id\"><code>Animation.id</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Récupère et défini le <code>String</code> utilisé pour identifier l'animation.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"animation.playstate_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/playState\"><code>Animation.playState</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"Cette valeur ne peut pas être changée.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Lecture seule </span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Retourne une valeur énumérée qui décit l'état de lecture de l'animation.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl><!---->\n<dl>\n  <dt id=\"animation.playbackrate_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/playbackRate\"><code>Animation.playbackRate</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Retourne et défini la fréquence de lecture de l'animation.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl><!---->\n<dl>\n  <dt id=\"animation.ready_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/ready\"><code>Animation.ready</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"Cette valeur ne peut pas être changée.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Lecture seule </span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Retourne la <code>Promise</code> prête en cours pour l'animation.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl><!---->\n<dl>\n  <dt id=\"animation.starttime\"><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/Animation/startTime\"><code>Animation.startTime</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Retourne et défini le moment prévu auquel la lecture de l'animation devrait commencer.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl><!---->\n<dl>\n  <dt id=\"animation.timeline_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/timeline\"><code>Animation.timeline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Retourne et défini la <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationTimeline\"><code>timeline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> associée à cette animation.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"gestionnaire_dévénements","title":"Gestionnaire d'événements","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"animation.oncancel_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/cancel_event\"><code>Animation.oncancel</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Retourne et définit le gestionnaire d'évènement pour l'évènement <code>cancel</code> (annuler).</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"animation.onfinish_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/finish_event\"><code>Animation.onfinish</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Retourne et définit le gestionnaire d'évènement pour l'évènement <code>finish</code> (terminer).</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"méthodes","title":"Méthodes","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"animation.cancel_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/cancel\"><code>Animation.cancel()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Supprime toutes les <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/KeyframeEffect\"><code>keyframeEffects</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> dues à cette animation et interomp la lecture.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl><!---->\n<dl>\n  <dt id=\"animation.finish_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/finish\"><code>Animation.finish()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Cherche la fin de l'animation, en fonction que l'animation soit en lecture normale ou inversée.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl><!---->\n<dl>\n  <dt id=\"animation.pause_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/pause\"><code>Animation.pause()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Suspend la lecture de l'animation.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl><!---->\n<dl>\n  <dt id=\"animation.play_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/play\"><code>Animation.play()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Démarre ou reprend la lecture de l'animation, ou redémarre l'animation au début si celle-ci est déjà terminée.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl><!---->\n<dl>\n  <dt id=\"animation.reverse_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/reverse\"><code>Animation.reverse()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Inverse la direction de lecture, en s'arrêtant au début de l'animation. Si l'animation est terminée ou annulée, elle sera jouée de la fin vers le début.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Spécifications","id":"spécifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://drafts.csswg.org/web-animations-1/#the-animation-interface","title":"Web Animations"}],"query":"api.Animation"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Compatibilité des navigateurs","id":"compatibilité_des_navigateurs","isH3":false,"query":"api.Animation","dataURL":"/fr/docs/Web/API/Animation/bcd.json"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Constructeur","id":"constructeur"},{"text":"Propriétés","id":"propriétés"},{"text":"Méthodes","id":"méthodes"},{"text":"Spécifications","id":"spécifications"},{"text":"Compatibilité des navigateurs","id":"compatibilité_des_navigateurs"}],"summary":"L'interface Animation de l'API Web Animations correspond à un lecteur d'animations et offre les commandes nécessaires au contrôle et à la chronologie d'un noeud ou d'une source d'animation.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Animation","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Animation","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Animation","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Animation","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Animation","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Animation","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"fr/web/api/animation","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/fr/web/api/animation/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/fr/docs/Web","title":"Technologies web pour développeurs"},{"uri":"/fr/docs/Web/API","title":"Référence Web API"},{"uri":"/fr/docs/Web/API/Animation","title":"Animation"}],"pageTitle":"Animation - Référence Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}